{"tid":1323413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑警」用完即棄！ 法國政府出賣鎮壓「黃背心」的警隊","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:26:13.000Z","uid":134071,"like":149,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c56158d78e2426e1414d4e7369457ed73e948107","tid":1323413,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"信報今日指中央研設獨立調查委員會, 其實唔奇.<br />\n<br />\n法國警察使用超暴力鎮壓「黃背心」革命, 令多名示威者傷亡. &nbsp;<br />\n而家, 「黃背心」革命確定慘敗後, 法國政府立即成立專家小組, 調查法國警隊處理「黃背心」示威的手法.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379829/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2379829%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=c15ec3cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379829/</a><br />\n<br />\n法審視警方處理「黃背心」手法<br />\n發佈時間: 2019/06/19<br />\n<br />\n法國持續多月的黃背心示威浪潮減弱，政府宣布成立專家小組，審視警方處理示威運動的手法。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者曾使用燒車、投擲汽油彈等暴力方式示威；警方武力程度不遑多讓，曾使用橡膠彈及防暴手榴彈等。<strong>內政部長卡斯塔內周一宣布成立15人專家小組，調查警方處理示威手法。</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威持續近半年仍未完全結束，但聲勢已大為減弱，據內政部數據，最近周末全國示威人數降至只得7,000，較11月高峰期的逾30萬人大幅減少。"},{"pid":"b462031c9288acbc2426e9b101d343b305b31150","tid":1323413,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n信報專欄：中央研設獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1322482/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1322482/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n明報:「黃背心」勇武革命 被法國政府擊敗的原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1322716/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1322716/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f393efe2c8f59f7af6b533cd198c111d673e6e23","tid":1323413,"uid":277186,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"睇到點解叫你藍色condom未呀 狗警"},{"pid":"b13d00b658a66ddca9ec0088940f2ae7068acd55","tid":1323413,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RtMcnU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RtMcnU</a>"},{"pid":"e3ff68311d08d149308a0a10a101e02440e5a815","tid":1323413,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af31b06d59fa0485176dda6f81af0f1ed1d49a5","tid":1323413,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0f8b63a64b689ff3a9c512774f4bd092b58def","tid":1323413,"uid":61653,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"遲早有一日清算黑警"},{"pid":"5a506b9ecc871bee6995dd60360de9463ac9c7ff","tid":1323413,"uid":80725,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"實比人清算 唔洗諗 全部condom"},{"pid":"4777f10086f87f2cda9438a4a97efeed5bd3363f","tid":1323413,"uid":79182,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"支持香港政府根據國際標準制定委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3572d465acb2c83ff388426086f9a690880bbac1","tid":1323413,"uid":211461,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭：絕不出賣黑警"},{"pid":"0da86127ae05e719d15c1fe2a4f3fd11b6ec688d","tid":1323413,"uid":28831,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"香港會閪咩<br />\n佢夠膽查真係比黑警反佢枱"},{"pid":"3e2c35cb48b03ff7ab71f77f0edd3b230c61abf6","tid":1323413,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"要send呢個post比「撐警群組」 &nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19809bde8bd35d93c99cd6ca68f1907870b5b5f4","ti